reviewText: Very creatively put together.  Love all his songs!!  I played this DVD for my guests and they loved it too.
I know Victor since he was a littlekid. His father is a good friend. We grew up in that neighborhood.
Victor se boto con este musical, muy bueno y Tremendo regalo para los puertorriquenos en el extranjero! excelente. Diferente a otros musicales, muy original.

Great DVD, full of joyous music and many other talented musicians are on it. I bought it for the Christmas Holidays, and we all enjoyed watching, listening to the great show and music in it. This is a Christmas Holiday DVD, SO YOU CAN GET IT AHEAD OF THE FOLLOWING HOLIDAYS AND ENJOY IT!!

As much as I like Victor Manuelle, I was so disappointed with this presentation.  While the music was good the dialog and staging was silly and uncharacteric of the Puerto Rican people.  The women with hair rollers in the street are a thing of the past and for good reason; its ugly - and so was the outfitting of the rest of the cast, with the exception of Victor Manuelle.  I have no problems with jeans or t-shirts but mismatched silly outfits - no!!!  I would have given it one star, but I don't like to use the word hate.
I highly recommend this item, it's a great deal and a great price...will shop again.....person I bought it for really loved it....
The music is ok but too much acting or talking on the concert!!!:(( I'll not recoment this to anyone,thanks. Hablan demasido en el show.
Victor Manuelle se consagra no solo como el sonero de la juventud, sino tambien como un cantante de pueblo que con su humildad hizo que este show fuera un rotundo exito.
